me.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Karen-Carpenter-and-Nandi-Bushell.-CREDIT_-Tony-Russell_Redferns-and-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-FF-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nandi-bushell">南迪·布谢尔 (Nandi Bushell)</a>分享了她对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carpenters">凯伦·卡彭特 (Karen Carpenter</a> ) 标志性表演“街头跳舞”的看法。看看下面。</p><p> 1968 年，卡彭特在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Eq3V2AfD9ec" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Your All American College Show</em></a>的录音室观众面前，以鼓手和主唱的身份演绎了这首热门歌曲。当时她只有 16 岁，比现在的布谢尔大两岁。</p><p> “我非常爱和尊重凯伦·卡彭特！”布谢尔在 X/Twitter 上写道。 “她是一位令人难以置信的鼓手、歌手、词曲作者。绝对的传奇！我收到的这个视频剪辑比其他任何视频剪辑都多，所以我想尝试一下她精彩的独奏。”</p><p>布谢尔的封面覆盖了卡彭特最初表演的镜头，因此可以看到两人同时演奏。这位 14 岁的女孩主要以鼓神童而闻名，但她也展示了她的声乐能力。看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯伦·卡彭特 vs 南迪·布谢尔 - 鼓独奏 #drumsolo" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BgJJuAhmNMg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Bushell 在五岁的时候就开始打鼓，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-concedes-defeat-in-drum-battle-with-nandi-bushell-this-kid-is-a-force-of-nature-2822083">在 2020 年因与 Foo Fighters 的戴夫·格罗尔 (Dave Grohl) 的在线鼓战而名声大噪，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nandi-bushell-responds-to-dave-grohls-admission-of-defeat-its-been-an-honour-battling-you-2823075">格罗尔甚至在当年 11 月承认失败</a>。</p><p>格罗尔后来称赞布谢尔，称观看她的表演“与任何<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队的</a>唱片、任何<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">齐柏林飞艇</a>唱片、任何<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ac-dc">AC/DC</a>唱片、任何<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队的</a>唱片一样鼓舞人心”。</p><p> 2021 年，她在洛杉矶一场演出《Everlong》时认识了喷火战机乐队，已故的泰勒·霍金斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-moment-nandi-bushell-finally-met-foo-fighters-3031066">送给她一对鼓槌</a>。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358#:~:text=Liam%20Gallagher%20tapped%20into%20the,Pretenders%2C%20all%20bands%20that%20Hawkins">这位鼓手</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-drummer-taylor-hawkins-has-died-3190788">于 2022 年去世（享年 50 岁）</a>后，她继续在他的悼念音乐会上表演了《Learn To Fly》。</p><p>现在，Bushell 已成为一名社交媒体明星，她定期发布自己翻唱各种歌曲的视频，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">The Who</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>等歌曲。她还发行了多首原创曲目，例如“The Shadows”、“Gods and Unicorns”和“Into the Abyss”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3467499" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3467499" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3467499" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty.jpg" alt="南迪·布谢尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nandi-bushell-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3467499" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：杰夫·斯派塞/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>除了鼓和声乐之外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nandi-bushells-delicate-piano-led-cover-of-nine-inch-nails-hurt-3782265">Bushell 最近还展示了她的钢琴技巧</a>，以细腻、安静的方式演绎了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">九寸钉 (Nine Inch Nails)</a> 1994 年的经典歌曲《Hurt》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-tom-morello-and-nandi-bushell-cover-john-lennons-power-to-the-people-at-download-3766423">布谢尔出现在今年六月的下载音乐节上</a>，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">汤姆·莫雷洛</a>一起演奏<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬</a>的《Power To The People》，您可以在下面观看。</p><p>她已经习惯了出现在大批观众面前，就在几个月前，作为 Young Voices 青年合唱团巡演的一部分， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nandi-bushell-perform-a-rock-medley-at-the-o2-in-front-of-20000-people-3603132">她在伦敦 O2 体育场演奏了一段长达 10 分钟的摇滚鼓混合曲</a>。</p><p>今年早些时候，Bushell 出现在 YouTube 上的 Drumeo 频道上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nandi-bushell-play-drums-to-twisted-sisters-were-not-gonna-take-it-as-she-hears-it-for-first-time-3558476">，与 Twisted Sisters 的《We’re Not Gonna Take It》一起演奏，但他以前从未听过这首歌</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-nandi-bushell-cover-karen-carpenters-iconic-dancing-in-the-street-3825537">聆听 Nandi Bushell 翻唱 Karen Carpenter 标志性歌曲《Dancing in The Street》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
前活结乐队鼓手杰伊·温伯格正在制作个人专辑https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-is-working-on-a-solo-album-3825531?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ex-slipknot-drummer-杰伊·温伯格正在制作个人专辑Surej SinghThu, 02 Jan 2025 05:50:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3825531 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Weinberg 于 2023 年底离开 Slipknot，此后一直为自杀倾向鼓吹</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-is-working-on-a-solo-album-3825531">前活结乐队鼓手杰伊·温伯格 (Jay Weinberg) 正在制作一张</a>首张发表在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的个人专辑。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">活结乐队</a>前鼓手杰伊·温伯格透露，他计划今年录制一张个人专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-anniversary-tour-new-album-look-outside-your-window-3822347">小丑谈论 Slipknot 25 周年巡演和未来：“我们现在可能有几张专辑”</a></strong></li></ul><p>温伯格于 2014 年加入 Slipknot，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-departure-of-drummer-jay-weinberg-3531261">于 2023 年 11 月被爱荷华州金属公司解雇</a>。他于 12 月 31 日在社交媒体上分享了他的新年计划。</p><p>虽然温伯格<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-joins-suicidal-tendencies-3597073">现在是朋克传奇乐队“自杀倾向”的鼓手</a>，但他表示今年他计划“在录音室录制更多音乐”。这似乎将成为他的首个个人项目——他说这个项目已经酝酿多年，而且似乎也会看到他弹吉他。 </p><figure id="attachment_3531467" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3531467" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3531467" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/jay-weinberg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3531467" class="wp-caption-text">杰·温伯格 (Jay Weinberg) 与活结乐队 (Slipknot) 一起表演。图片来源：Venla Shalin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>他在 Instagram 上写道：“我 2025 年的目标之一是在录音室录制更多音乐——从我自己已经写了很长一段时间的材料开始。其中一些是我从 20 岁出头就开始努力的。</p><p>他继续说道：“从那以后我就再也没有碰过这些歌曲，直到最近我才感受到灵感，重新拿起吉他，再次弹奏这些东西。这是一次充实的经历，我告诉你——我开始喜欢这些歌曲的发展方向。最终决定在来年发行一些新音乐，感觉很好。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DENrDX3JG61/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M