9436">将于六月恢复欧洲巡演</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/slipknot-tickets/artist/763913?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=QUKVXO0SNxyNUr-wIeURt2waUkCScqVtY1o00M0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559">请访问此处获取门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3824238" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824238" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824238" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270.jpg" alt="活结乐队 (Slipknot) 的科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 于 2024 年 12 月 20 日在伦敦 O2 体育馆表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Slipknot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824238" class="wp-caption-text">活结乐队的科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 于 2024 年 12 月 20 日在伦敦 O2 体育馆表演。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-anniversary-tour-new-album-look-outside-your-window-3822347">Slipknot 乐队的 Clown 接受<em>NME</em>采访</a>，分享了乐队期待已久的“失落”专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-look-outside-your-window-management-has-it-coming-out-3823025">《Look Outside Your Window》的最新消息。</a>该唱片由创始成员兼打击乐手（真名 Shawn Crahan）与 Corey Taylor、Sid Wilson 和 Jim Root 录制，当时他们正在制作 2008 年的“All Hope Is Gone”。近年来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-release-11-psychedelic-outtake-songs-hope-gone-soon-2540336">该专辑的发行一直受到乐队的嘲笑</a>，尽管尚未取得任何成果。</p><p> “我确实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">[去年对<em>《NME》</em>说</a>]将于 2024 年举行，今年我尽了最大努力争取成功，”他说。 “我可以告诉你的是，两天前我向科里展示了最终的艺术作品。它正在发生，但不幸的是，由于圣诞节和新年以及商业运作方式，我今年无法将其推迟。</p><p> “但我向你保证，现在一切都不再由我掌控了。它正在继续推进，钱已经花掉了，并且有一个计划。管理层已经掌握了它，并且即将推出。” </p><figure id="attachment_3822353" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822353" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822353" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270.jpg" alt="活结乐团的肖恩·“小丑”·克拉汉将于 2024 年演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Clown-Slipknot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3822353" class="wp-caption-text">活结乐团的肖恩·“小丑”·克拉汉将于 2024 年表演。图片来源：Andrew Benge/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在最新的<em>《NME》</em>对 Clown 的采访中，这位打击乐手反思了 Slipknot 的新材料计划。</p><p> “埃洛伊（卡萨格兰德，鼓手）在乐队里，我们九个人之间现在正在发生一些非常有趣的事情，”他说。 “很多东西都在流传，我们现在可能有几张专辑。至于感觉如何，我现在对你完全诚实，就像云已经离开了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-slipknot-drummer-jay-weinberg-is-working-on-a-solo-album-3825531">前活结乐队鼓手杰伊·温伯格 (Jay Weinberg) 正在制作一张</a>首张发表在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的个人专辑。</p> ;
